# Loyalty — Cron Points Expiry Trigger
# M10-S08: GCP Cloud Scheduler calls this endpoint at 02:00 UTC daily.
# In production this is called by GCP Cloud Scheduler (network-protected).
# M115-S03 adds CronAuthGuard (OIDC token from GCP Cloud Scheduler).
#
# Prerequisites:
#   1. pnpm infra:up
#   2. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run migration:run
#   3. pnpm --filter @ikaro/backend run dev

@baseUrl = {{backendUrl}}

### POST /cron/loyalty-expiry — run daily points expiry
POST {{baseUrl}}/cron/loyalty-expiry

###
